quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,44,"Ndipo anthu okhala ku Paradiso adzaitana anthu a ku Moto. “Ndithudi chimene adatilonjeza ife Ambuye wathu tachipeza kuti ndi choona. Kodi inu mwapeza chomwe adakulonjezani Ambuye wanu kuti ndi choona?” Iwo adzati: Inde. Ndipo wofuula adzanena pakati pawo: “Matemberero a Mulungu ali pa anthu olakwa.”"
  7,45,Iwo amene anali kuletsa anzawo kutsatira njira ya Mulungu ndipo amafuna kuti iyo ikhale yokhotakhota ndipo adalibe chikhulupiriro m’moyo umene uli nkudza
  7,46,"Ndipo pakati pawo padzakhala chotchinga ndi chipupa mmene mudzakhala anthu amene adzazindikira wina aliyense poona zizindikiro zawo. Iwo adzaitana anthu a ku Paradiso: Mtendere ukhale pa inu. Koma panthawi imeneyo iwo adzakhala asadalowe ku Paradiso koma iwo adzakhala ndi chikhulupiriro choti adzalowanso mopanda chikaiko"
  7,47,"Ndipo pamene iwo adzaona iwo amene adzakhala ku moto, iwo adzati: “Oh Ambuye wathu! Musatiike ife malo a anthu oipa.”"
  7,48,"Ndipo anthu a m’chipupa adzawaitana anthu omwe adzawadziwa ndi zizindikiro zawo ndipo adzati: “Kodi kuchuluka kwanu, kwakuthandizani chiani ndiponso mwano umene mumaonetsa ku chipembedzo?”"
  7,49,"Kodi awa ndi anthu amene munkalumbira kuti sadzalandira chisomo cha Mulungu? “Lowani ku Paradiso, inu simudzachita mantha ndiponso simudzada nkhawa ayi.”"
  7,50,"Ndipo anthu a ku Moto adzaitana anthu a ku Paradiso kuti, “Tithireni madzi kapena china chilichonse chimene Mulungu wakupatsani inu!” Anthu a ku Paradiso adzati, “Mulungu adaletsa zonse ziwiri kuti anthu osakhulupirira alandire.”"
  7,51,“Iwo amene adasandutsa chipembedzo chawo ngatinthabwalandichoseweretsandipoadalikunyengedwa ndi zokoma za m’moyo wa padziko lapansi. Motero lero Ife tiwaiwala monga mmene adaiwalira za kukumana kwa tsiku lawoli ndi chifukwa chokana zizindikiro zathu.”